# JaCoCo 汇总报告（mvn verify 生成于仓库根目录 coverage-reports/{artifactId}/，以及子目录的错位输出）
/coverage-reports/
**/coverage-reports/
# JaCoCo 原始 exec 数据（mvn verify/verify 中间产物，模块根目录）
**/jacoco.exec
**/jacoco-it.exec
**/jacoco-merged.exec

######################
# Flattened POM
######################
.flattened-pom.xml
/.history/

######################
# Mavis .harness runtime
######################
# Each rein's opencode/ subtree is auto-generated by the Mavis daemon on first
# agent spawn (opencode.json, package.json, node_modules/, plugins/, tools/).
# It's machine-local runtime state, not source — keep it out of git.
# Only the agent.md files under .harness/reins/<name>/ are version-controlled.
/.harness/reins/*/opencode/
/.omo/
